The true up calculation is: 

{{Total Overcharge * (Pct of current year player has spent with assignor Club ("PCTCY") / (Prior years/fractional years spent with assignor Club + PCTCY))}}

Some example calculations from prior trades:


{{<<Woo-Suk Go Calculation:>> $99,462 * (19.9% / (0 + 19.9%)) = $99,462 Refund }}



{{<<Canha Calculation:>> $1,083,333 * (66.7% / (1 + 66.7%)) = $433,333 Refund}}

These credits will only be applied if the trade happens in season and if the true up is a refund (negative value)
